longBusinessSummary: Cocoon Holdings Limited is a principal investment firm specializing in investments in listed and unlisted companies. The firm typically invests in the fields of resources, technology enabled manufacturing, food and retail and healthcare. It also offers other investment services that include money market instruments, capital syndication, and arranging strategic corporate deals, with an emphasis on financial restructuring and capital infusion. The firm invests in Asia and the Greater China region. Cocoon Holdings Limited, formerly known as Huge China Holdings Limited, was founded in 1993 and is based in Hong Kong with additional office in Hamilton, Bermuda.
